OL,3,CHow the world's first diamond battery
OL,4,Ccould provide power for thousands of
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe battery is made from lab grown
OL,8,Fsynthetic diamonds, as ITV News
OL,9,FScience Correspondent Martin Stew
OL,10,Freports.
OL,12,FScientists in the UK have created the
OL,13,Fworld's first diamond battery, capable
OL,14,Fof producing power for thousands of
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FIt's made from lab grown synthetic
OL,18,Fdiamonds, which encase a radioactive
OL,19,Felement called Carbon-14.
