OL,3,CHow the world's first diamond battery
OL,4,Ccould provide power for thousands of
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FAs it decays, fast moving electrons
OL,8,Fare emitted. The battery uses those to
OL,9,Fcreate electricity in much the same
OL,10,Fway a solar panel uses light particles.
OL,12,FCompared to a normal lithium or
OL,13,Falkaline battery which may last a few
OL,14,Fmonths, the half life of Carbon-14 is
OL,15,Fso long that in 5,000 years a diamond
OL,16,Fbattery would still be at 50% power.
OL,18,FStephen Wheeler from the UK Atomic
OL,19,FEnergy Authority told me there is huge
OL,20,Fpotential for the future.
