OL,3,CHow the world's first diamond battery
OL,4,Ccould provide power for thousands of
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"This technology is particularly
OL,8,Fsuitable for places you can't access -
OL,9,Fif it's in space, or sub-sea, or you
OL,10,Fdon't want to access it because it's
OL,11,Fin a hazardous environment," he said.
OL,13,FThat could include inside the human
OL,14,Fbody, for devices like pacemakers,
OL,15,Fhearing aids and even implants in your
OL,16,Feyes.
OL,18,FMr Wheeler added: "This is one area
OL,19,Fthat you feel you're actually making a
OL,20,Fpositive impacts."
