OL,3,CHow the world's first diamond battery
OL,4,Ccould provide power for thousands of
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"They can incinerate it, take out the
OL,8,FCarbon-14 back and reuse it, so it
OL,9,Fliterally gives us no waste at all -
OL,10,Fone of the reasons it's good for the
OL,11,Fplanet."
OL,13,FScientists at the University of
OL,14,FBristol are now experimenting with
OL,15,Fdifferent radioactive elements to make
OL,16,Fthe batteries more powerful.
OL,18,FThe hope is to create something
OL,19,Fcommercially scalable this century.
